178
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:06,370
That's right. Taking on the world is no easy task.

179
00:15:06,370 --> 00:15:10,400
We would like to be the top travel agency in the world someday.

180
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:13,680
The world's top travel agency? I'd like that!



181
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:26,510
