Just splendid.

191
00:16:13,450 --> 00:16:14,690
Sorry.

192
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:21,650
I was just thinking how splendid it would be to travel to Yugoslavia with someone like you.

193
00:16:24,930 --> 00:16:27,670
