225
00:18:43,260 --> 00:18:48,150
Now wait! Why are you bending over backwards to get a job?




226
00:18:48,150 --> 00:18:51,420
Must you always be the aggressive reporter?

227
00:18:54,050 --> 00:18:57,900
I told you before that my first career choice was to be a travel agent.

228
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:01,970
Yeah, you want to work using your own abilities,

229
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:04,760
and you'll be able to see the world at a travel agency.

230
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:07,290
Isn't that great? I admire your motivation.

231
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:11,430
I actually have one more reason.

232
00:19:11,430 --> 00:19:12,750
I thought...

233
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:17,170
