234
00:19:17,170 --> 00:19:18,630
to search for my father.

235
00:19:25,850 --> 00:19:29,920
If I work at a travel agency, there's a chance I'll meet someone

236
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:34,230
who gave my dad a boarding pass or saw him at one of his destinations.

237
00:19:34,230 --> 00:19:35,880
Oh, yeah...





238
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:38,900
Th-That's good thinking.
 Don't you agree, Matsuda-san?

239
00:19:42,690 --> 00:19:45,170
Oh, no. I'm really going to be late!

240
00:19:54,250 --> 00:19:55,460
What should we do now?

241
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:58,380
