242
00:20:00,870 --> 00:20:02,560
If that's the case, then I'll take her to him!

243
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:05,070
I'm reuniting her with her dad!

244
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:08,810
Come on, Kazamatsuri!
 Tell me where Kojiro-san is!

245
00:20:08,810 --> 00:20:10,890
Where's Kojiro-san right now?

246
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:14,800
Kojiro-san is Sayaka-san's coach.

247
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:19,880
If you let Yawara-san see him, how do you think she'll react?

248
00:20:24,530 --> 00:20:27,570
Geez, why didn't you stop him from becoming her coach?

249
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:29,660
Sayaka-san practically begged him.

250
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:32,130
You think I could've stopped it?



251
00:20:32,130 --> 00:20:34,280
I was going to pick up the check, but forget it!

252
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:35,920
Pay for your own coffee.

253
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:39,830
<i>All Sports</i> really does pay you peanuts, doesn't it?

254
00:20:40,770 --> 00:20:43,460
I'll pay for Yawara-san's drink!

255
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:45,230
No need to strain yourself.

256
00:20:45,230 --> 00:20:47,860
You're paid below market, so I'll take care of it.

257
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:49,400
No, I will!


258
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,300
I have this!

259
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:50,960
No, you don't!

260
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:51,890
Yes I do!

261
00:21:00,810 --> 00:21:03,360
O-One more time, please.

262
00:21:05,990 --> 00:21:08,780
Come on. That's enough.

263
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:16,860
I have to go spar with the guys on the national team.

264
00:21:18,080 --> 00:21:19,710
Please!

265
00:21:20,580 --> 00:21:25,310
Just one more round! I think I'm beginning to understand!

266
00:21:26,130 --> 00:21:27,430
All right.

267
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:34,440
Un, deux, trois...

268
00:21:35,430 --> 00:21:38,270
So that's the Ito Fujiko I've been hearing about?



269
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:40,480
Yeah, she's pretty good, Yamashita.

270
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,270
Un!

271
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:45,580
Not only is she good, it's a waste of good talent to use her as just a training player!

272
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,780
Master Inokuma Jigoro, when did you get here?

273
00:21:47,780 --> 00:21:49,780
Deux!


274
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:54,440
Doesn't it taste great? 
This is Beanpole's home brew.

275
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,910
Oh, this is good.

276
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:59,090
Her tea is as good as her judo.

277
00:21:59,090 --> 00:22:01,690
Yes, only because I taught her well.

278
00:22:01,690 --> 00:22:03,940
She has the height and the balance.

279
00:22:03,940 --> 00:22:07,250
She'd be evenly matched with a foreign opponent. Right?

280
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:12,800
By the way, Director Yanagizawa, have you decided on the free-weight player yet?

281
00:22:13,210 --> 00:22:17,530
No, not yet. However, we'd really like it to be Yawara-san.

282
00:22:17,530 --> 00:22:19,140
Trois!

283
00:22:20,390 --> 00:22:22,300
Y-Yamada-san?

284
00:22:22,300 --> 00:22:23,640
His head took the entire blow!

285
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:25,020
Hey, are you all right, Yamada?

286
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:26,800
Nope, he's out like a light.

287
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:29,050
I'm sorry!

288
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:35,790
I'm sorry! Oh gosh, wait... why?

289
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:43,990
S-O-R-R-Y!

290
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:52,930
Sign: The Barcelona Olympics in 320 Days

291
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:56,850
We're finally going to Yugoslavia.

292
00:22:56,850 --> 00:22:58,820
Fujiko-san's really relishing this trip.

293
00:22:58,820 --> 00:23:00,970
Yeah, she should enjoy it while it lasts.

294
00:23:00,970 --> 00:23:02,870
What do you mean by that?

295
00:23:03,710 --> 00:23:05,810
This tatsuta-age is delicious!

296
00:23:05,810 --> 00:23:08,950
I know you're up to something, Grandpa.




297
00:23:08,950 --> 00:23:12,710
You can expect some very interesting developments.

298
00:23:12,710 --> 00:23:13,240
Yawara!

299
00:23:13,910 --> 00:23:16,780
The Opening Act of the Yugoslavia World Championships!

300
00:23:16,780 --> 00:23:17,790
You'll be getting my Harai Goshi if you don't watch!

301
00:23:17,790 --> 00:23:19,530
The Opening Act of the Yugoslavia World Championships!
You'll be getting my Harai Goshi if you don't watch!

302
00:23:19,530 --> 00:23:22,710
The Opening Act of the Yugoslavia World Championships!

303
00:23:31,760 --> 00:23:38,730
At twilight, my heart gently falls into a labyrinth.
tasogare ni maiorita kokoro no labyrinth

304
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:46,900
Thrills and sorrows swirl around me.
tokimeki to setsunasa ga mawari hajimeteru

305
00:23:47,730 --> 00:23:54,490
We're pushed and shoved as we cross the street.
hitonami no kousaten senaka osarenagara

306
00:23:54,490 --> 00:24:03,710
We climb an endless hill, just you and me.
sakamichi wo doko made mo anata to aruita

307
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:13,090
I want to say "I love you" to the one I truly want,
naze hoshii mono wo "daisuki" to

308
00:24:13,090 --> 00:24:20,390
But why can I not? I really don't know.
koe ni dashite ienai no?

309
00:24:20,390 --> 00:24:26,150
You're standing here by my side.
ima anata ga iru

310
00:24:26,450 --> 00:24:36,410
That fact alone puts my worries to rest.
tada sore dake de yasuragu kimochi

311
00:24:36,410 --> 00:24:43,410
"Please don't let go of the hand you're holding,"
"tsunaideru sono yubi wo hanasanaide..."

312
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:50,800
I say as I look for your smile.
egao wo sagashite

